As BLacknightmare said the the room glowed and began to change as a dark red 
light began to show all around. Suddenly a light blue orb, a dark green orb, 
and a red porb appeared before her. Each lifeless. THe bright blue orb then 
floats on over to her.

Ball: "When a member of the Infecticon race dies it goes to a dimension. Each 
of these orbs represents that dimension, the blue one represents the matrix, 
the green represents the void, and the last represents Bamphomet. Which of 
these orbs is the correct dimension?"

Blights smirks and looks to Darkfate.

Blight: "She has failed the first test. Only two left. It does not look like 
she will make it."

--part1_125.1b8e91d.288466cc_boundary
